A big thank you to the authors of the following works that helped me create Procrastinate
No More:

Concept
=======

The concept of this widget is based on a Python Applet called Tomate:
https://gitorious.org/tomate/pages/Home

Source code
===========

The source code of the following widgets were helpful when coding Procrastinate No More:

Activity Manager Plasmoid - used as a starting point.
http://kde-look.org/content/show.php/Activity+Manager+Plasmoid?content=136278

Toggle-Compositing - to see how to draw the icons.
http://kde-look.org/content/show.php/Toggle-Compositing?content=78299

Bubblemon - to solve the sizing issues and handle themes.
(part of kdeplasma-addons)

Icons
=====

The icons are derived from the Oxygen icon theme (http://www.oxygen-icons.org/) and licensed
under the Creative Common Attribution-ShareAlike 3.0 License and the GNU Library General
Public License.

